            "title": "滬指開市跌6點 深成指跌46點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段回吐，上證綜指以4075點開市，跌6點或0.15%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14920點，亦跌46點或0.31%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數跌6點或0.15%，開報4750點；創業板指數開市報3662點，跌15點或0.42%。</p>\n</div>",
