            "title": "勝宏科技超購430倍  一手中籤率0.71%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">勝宏科技(02476)公布招股結果，招股價209.88元，公開招股超額認購430.15倍。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">一手中籤率0.71%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"勝宏科技招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/02476.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"勝宏科技招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/02476.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">勝宏科技招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際配售超額認購17.5倍。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資額201.77億元，集資淨額198.89億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">勝宏科技(02476)暗盤收升58%至60%，最多曾升近74%，一手帳面賺逾12300元。輝立暗盤收升58.66%，報333元，一手100股帳面賺12312元。最高見365元，升73.9%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15898635-%e5%8b%9d%e5%ae%8f%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e8%b6%85%e8%b3%bc430%e5%80%8d-%e4%b8%80%e6%89%8b%e4%b8%ad%e7%b1%a4%e7%8e%870-71",
